name: Feeling Lonely, but Shadows Dancing With Me
description:
When I was traveling alone to the south coast of West Java on a motorcycle. Just heal from my study. There I questioned about anything. About achievement, about the future, about success. The beach was so quiet, I didn't find anyone, but the waves were so wild.

This photo was taken in Cipatujah, southern Tasikmalaya, Indonesia in 2018.
